snippet.textDisplay: Three  unique voices finally brought together for right kind of song and they sang it perfectly and fun was had by all. Credit must go to the whole team and especially Ali Hamza finally has come out of the shadow of brother Ali Noor and shows he can be great director not just a voice...love it...Sethi is finally having some fun after Ranjish...Waqar was fantastic and sang it with energy and compassion. Waqar Ehsin where have u been all this time in  'zamane Puraney' mein...This was perfect song of the season and burned all tapes...so to speak..Sethi Ali Waqar gave three distinct flavors to make it perfect.
